originalText.text: The Musicians Foundation is an incredible non profit organization. Musicians all over the country lost revenue due to Covid. The Musicians Foundation is a life saver in many different circumstances. Mine was dental and i was awarded a grant to help with expenses. in this day and age it is nice to know that someone really cares for your wellbeing. Thank you once again and keep up the good work, i know a lot of musicians do not know of your grants. We will change that.

originalText.text: The Musicians Foundation is an amazing organization that values hardworking artists and jumps in to provide aid in time of need. They have an extraordinary mission in realizing that artists are people with the same struggles as anyone else, and that we have few resources in non music-educational aid. They have assisted in times of crisis. Bravo!
